Look up airport information

get_metar_stn.Rd

Look up airport information

get_metar_stn(
  id.icao = metar.stn$icao,
  fi.name = ".+",
  fi.icao = ".+",
  fi.ctry = ".+",
  fi.lat = c(-90, 90),
  fi.lon = c(-180, 180),
  is.active = TRUE
)

Arguments

id.icao

Vector of ICAO identifiers
fi.name

Lorem Ipsum
fi.icao

Lorem Ipsum
fi.ctry

Lorem Ipsum
fi.lat

Lorem Ipsum
fi.lon

Lorem Ipsum
is.active

Filter by active stations

Author

M. Saenger

Examples

# By ICAO Identifier
get_metar_stn(id.icao = c("LSZH", "YSSY"))

#>    icao ctry ctry3   ctry_name region            ap_name_long        lon
#> 1: LSZH   CH   CHE Switzerland     ZH Zurich-Kloten|Oberglatt   8.535833
#> 2: YSSY   AU   AUS   Australia    NSW         Sydney|Kyeemagh 151.173056
#>          lat  elev       ap_name synop iata active
#> 1:  47.47972 426.3 Zurich-Kloten    NA <NA>   TRUE
#> 2: -33.94639   6.4        Sydney    NA <NA>   TRUE
# Central Europe
get_metar_stn(fi.icao = "^L", fi.lon = c(5, 11), fi.lat = c(46, 49))
